    # Overview

    This is a dataset about Divisions, Districts and Sub Districts in Bangladesh in SQL format

    # Tables

    The code below creates respective three tables and inserts location data to them.

    # Division Table

    CREATE TABLE `divisions` (
  `id` int(1) NOT NULL,
  `name` varchar(25) NOT NULL,
  `bn_name` varchar(25) NOT NULL,
  `url` varchar(50) NOT NULL
);

ALTER TABLE `divisions`
  ADD PRIMARY KEY (`id`);
